snippet: Protest leaders in Islamabad said Wednesday that their supporters would vacate the Parliament area, where they converged last week, after violent clashes with the police.
abstract: Pakistani protest leaders in Islamabad say their supporters will vacate the Parliament area in Islamabad, after violent clashes with the police.
